{"tid":2241660,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"天文學家捕捉黑洞吞噬星體過程 撕成意粉狀","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T14:38:23.000Z","uid":294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b303a7f53d3cd528e57c43e020991a694169bd1","tid":2241660,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"最近，終於有天文學家成功捕捉到黑洞吞噬星體的過程。<br />\n位於智利聖地亞哥的歐洲南天文台（European Southern Observatory）周一（12日）發新聞稿表示，有天文學家研究團隊成功拍攝到星體被吸進黑洞過程，這次吞噬位於波江座 （Eridanus constellation），距離地球約2.15億光年。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊指出，整個吞噬過程持續超過六個月，星體在巨大引力下，被扯向黑洞的方向；影像清楚展示星體被撕裂，變成意大利粉一樣的麵條狀。星體被吞噬瓦解時，會釋放出強大的光芒和能量，令遠在地球的天文學家都可通過望遠鏡，在星體消失前發現星體。<br />\n<br />\n今次被吞噬的星體質量與太陽差不多，而星體被瓦解後，並沒有被完全毀滅，目前還剩下約一半的質量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AKCp-1OGGP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAKCp-1OGGP4&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=9461dc38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AKCp-1OGGP4</a>"},{"pid":"497a0479b83e129176e3d81eac7ee0a029bc7ccd","tid":2241660,"uid":295230,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"飛天意粉神既證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e5901216d73fc96dd9d95158fbae0561190af9","tid":2241660,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"係RT比人話係假"},{"pid":"2f5f6387e1a0e679f2a39ad9c96b337d93a94858","tid":2241660,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"好似提緊你煮熟 食得咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7c611a982876fe8f5db5be0047927391d96d2e","tid":2241660,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:52:32.000Z",